               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Dāwit “Psalter” (fols. 3r-130vb)
 I-1) Mazmura Dāwit “Psalms of
                     David” (fols. 3r-103v), incomplete 
 I-2) Maḥālǝya nabiyāt “The Canticles
                     of the Prophets” (fols. 104r-114v) 
 I-3) Maḥālǝya maḥālǝy “Song of Songs”
                     (fols. 115r-121r) 
 I-4) Wǝddāse Māryām “Praise of Mary” (fols.
                     123ra-130vb), incomplete
 
 Additiones 1-8.</summary>
