                        <list type="abbreviations">
                           <item>Text I-4</item>
                           <item>ሰ፡ ለ፡ ቅ፡ for ሰአሊ፡ ለነ፡ ቅድስት</item>
                           <item>Words or their abbreviations stand for the whole refrain.</item>
                           <item>
                              <abbr>ሠ፡</abbr> for <expan>ሠረቀ፡ በሥጋ፡ እምድንግል፡ ዘእንበለ፡ ዘርአ፡ ብእሲ፡ ወአድኅነነ
                              </expan> (<locus target="#123ra">123ra</locus>)</item>
                           <item>
                              <abbr>እስ፡/እስመ፡</abbr> for <expan>እስመ፡ በፈቃዱ፡ ወበሥምረቱ፡ አቡሁ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡
