                        <seg type="rubrication">Nomina sacra (name of St Mary in Text I-4); titles
                           and numbers of the Pss., Canticles and Songs; title of Texts I-2 and I-3;
                           title and incipit of the daily readings of Text I-4; name, number and
                           traditional interpretation of the Hebrew letters in Ps. 118; elements of
                           the punctuation signs and text dividers; Ethiopic numerals or their
                           elements.
 
 A few groups of lines (alternating with black lines)
                           on the incipit page of Text I-1.</seg>
